		"description": "DOCUMENTATION: No description is available for this CVE. \n            STATEMENT: The PostgreSQL JDBC Driver is not affected in the default query mode. Users that do not override the query mode are not impacted.\n            MITIGATION: Do not use the connection propertypreferQueryMode=simple. If you do not explicitly specify a query mode then you are using the default of extended and are not impacted by this issue.",
